             were indicted for <rs id="t18180617-181-off1009" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18180617-181-off1009" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180617-181-off1009" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18180617-181-cd1010" type="crimeDate">14th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180617-181-off1009 t18180617-181-cd1010"></join>, 100lbs of lead, belonging to the Worshipful the 
                     <persName id="t18180617-181-victim1484" type="victimName">
                        <rs id="t18180617-181-viclabel1011" type="occupation">Governor of St. Margaret's Hospital, Westminster</rs>
